      • addedLoad

        public java.lang.String addedLoad(int numBoxes,
                                  double weightBox,
                                  java.lang.String ownerRegNum,
                                  char typeLoad,
                                  double valuePaid)
        This method added a load.
        pre: The loads list is initialized.
        post: The new load has successfully registered.
        Parameters:
        numBoxes - Boxes to load.
        weightBox - Weight of one box.
        ownerRegNum - Nit of the owner. ownerRegNum != null && ownerRegNum != "".
        typeLoad - Type of load.
        valuePaid - value paid client.
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception -
        1. The commercial registration number entered does not match any customer. 2. Load container is at its limit.
